div.p:
Concerning the meaning of these words, This is my body; Let that Apoththegme of Q. Elizabeth bee much thought-on; who beeing examined (in her sisters Raigne) about the Reall presence,

and in great danger, made this Answer (which 'tis said saved her life)


Christ tooke the bread and brake it;

Hee was The Word, that spake it;

And what that Word did make it;

I doe receive and take it;
